Package com.google.api.client.http

Added Classes and Interfaces
BackOffPolicy Strategy interface to control back off between retry attempts.
BasicAuthentication Basic authentication HTTP request initializer as specified in Basic Authentication Scheme
ExponentialBackOffPolicy Implementation of BackOffPolicy that increases the back off period for each retry attempt using a randomization function that grows exponentially.
ExponentialBackOffPolicy.
Builder 		Builder for ExponentialBackOffPolicy.
 

Changed Classes and Interfaces
AbstractInputStreamContent Serializes HTTP request content from an input stream into an output stream.
ByteArrayContent Concrete implementation of AbstractInputStreamContent that generates repeatable input streams based on the contents of byte array.
FileContent Concrete implementation of AbstractInputStreamContent that generates repeatable input streams based on the contents of a file.
HttpContent Serializes HTTP request content into an output stream.
HttpRequest HTTP request.
HttpResponse HTTP response.
HttpResponseException Exception thrown when an error status code is detected in an HTTP response.
HttpStatusCodes Constants enumerating the HTTP status codes.
HttpUnsuccessfulResponseHandler Interface which handles abnormal HTTP responses (in other words not 2XX).
InputStreamContent Concrete implementation of AbstractInputStreamContent that simply handles the transfer of data from an input stream to an output stream.
LowLevelHttpRequest Low-level HTTP request.
MultipartRelatedContent Serializes MIME Multipart/Related content as specified by RFC 2387: The MIME Multipart/Related Content-type.
UriTemplate Expands URI Templates.
UrlEncodedContent Implements support for HTTP form content encoding serialization of type {@code application/x-www-form-urlencoded} as specified in the HTML 4.0 Specification.
UrlEncodedParser Implements support for HTTP form content encoding parsing of type {@code application/x-www-form-urlencoded} as specified in the HTML 4.0 Specification.
UrlEncodedParser.Builder Builder for UrlEncodedParser.
